35:06.438 --> 35:07.739
Yeah. I've been down there
a couple times.

35:07.773 --> 35:09.508
I like that race track
at Agua Caliente.

35:09.541 --> 35:10.576
You know that place?

35:10.609 --> 35:12.311
Yeah.
