36:28.854 --> 36:32.157
She started telling me
this kind of wild story.

36:32.190 --> 36:33.859
I didn't know
how much to believe.

36:33.892 --> 36:36.495
Well, what was the story?

36:36.528 --> 36:40.899
About this guy, this doctor
she knew from Oakland.

36:40.932 --> 36:44.202
He'd told her he was
gonna help her get clean,

36:44.236 --> 36:47.339
but he took her back
to the Bay Area,

36:47.373 --> 36:48.840
and then, when he got there,

36:48.874 --> 36:51.710
he just wanted her
for some kind of sex slave.

36:51.743 --> 36:53.512
So, what happened?
What did he do?

36:53.545 --> 36:55.281
He wanted to tie her up,

36:55.314 --> 36:59.385
but she talked him into
letting her tie him up instead.

36:59.418 --> 37:02.854
And then she busted him
in the head and got away.

37:02.888 --> 37:04.856
That's all she said.

37:04.890 --> 37:08.193
I guess it was
his phone she called me on.

37:08.226 --> 37:09.728
She thought that
